Company Description: Mcdonald S Is A Global Food Service Retailer That Operates More Than 30,000 Locations IN Over 100 Countries. The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Fish, Salads, Fruit And Sandwiches. With A Location IN Carle Place, N.Y., It Additionally Offers French Fries, Chicken Sandwiches, Quarter Pounders And Honey Wheat Rolls. The Restaurant S Menu Also Includes The Ranch Snack Wrap, Big N' Tasty, Chicken Selects And Mcflurry Treats. It Serves A Variety Of Beverages And Desserts, Including Chocolate Triple Thick, Minty Mudd Bath Triple Thick And Strawberry Triple Thick Shakes And Mcdonaldland Cookies. Mcdonald's Restaurants Are Owned And Operated By Independent Franchisees Of The Mcdonald's Corporation.

Established IN 1948, Mcdonald's Corp. Is One Of The Leading Foodservice Retailers IN The World. The Company Offers Various Food Items, Lunch Menus, Soft Drinks And Other Beverages. Additionally, It Serves Burgers, Sandwiches, Chicken, Salads, Snacks, Sides, Desserts And Shakes. Mcdonald's Also Provides Fries, Chicken Mcnuggets And Egg Mcmuffin, To Name A Few. The Company Is Serving More Than 60 Million People IN As Many As 117 Countries Every Day. It Also Provides Happy Meals, Extra-Value Meals, Dollar Menu And Mighty Kids Meals.
